Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,MY HAPPY MARRIAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 11\NMY MOTHER'S LEGACY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason your mother married\Ninto the Saimori family,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and why your supernatural abilities\Nwere sealed away til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.46,0:01:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It all started a few years\Nbefore you were born.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsuruki Trading had failed in negotiations\Nwith a major business partner.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were in a slump, the worst\Nsince the founding of the company.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.56,0:02:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We were facing a mountain of debt\Nthat was beyond our means.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the company was our main income,\Nthe situation was dire.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that crucial moment,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there was a family who approached us\Nwith a marriage arrangement offer.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From out of nowhere,\Nthey sensed the Usuba family's crisis{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and offered to take on a large amount\Nof the debt we had incurred.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All in exchange\Nfor marrying Sumi off to them.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was against it,\Nbut for every rejection letter I sent,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}they would reply with another proposal.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, things took a turn.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deciding not to consult me,\NSumi reached out to them{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and arranged the engagement\Nof her own volition.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand\Nwhat you've done with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And behind my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be passing on\Nthe Usuba bloodline
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to another house, Sumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If we try to leave things as they are,\Nthe Usubas will be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumi! You have no idea\Nwhat this means for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth could you even hope to do\Nwith your body in its current condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tell me what other option there is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.63,0:03:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want this. I'm sorry, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The household that\NSumi married into back then{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was the Saimori family.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After the so-called marriage arrangement\Nwas made official,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all lines of communication were cut.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From the day of her wedding,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sumi and I became completely estranged.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something\NI would like to show you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your ability is called Dream-Sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your gift is an ability\Neven Sumi wasn't capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's called Dream-Sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Place your hand on the bark of this tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:03:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I overheard that\Nshe's an Usuba or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.54,0:04:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's pretty withdrawn for a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't just a political marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.67,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand your role?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Our lineage will have\NUsuba blood through our child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Sumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was that...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She has Dream-Sight?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still unable to confirm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.06,0:05:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo is quite young.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't\Nobtain the Usuba's supernatural ability
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,as quickly as we're able,\Nthe Saimori family will soon be demoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about hardships we endured\Nto obtain the bloodline of that family.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If Miyo doesn't possess any abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,then you must rush\Nto produce another child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time\Nbefore Sumi passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Miyo.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It looks like\NI don't have very much time left.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With that kind of power,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.14,0:06:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}your gift will start\Nshowing signs before long.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When it does, your supernatural abilities{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will be endlessly exploited,\Nthen the Usubas would...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to live on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to do this,\Nbut you have to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.91,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have to live\Nthrough many painful experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You may try to blame yourself,\Nthinking being giftless is a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But for the time being,\NI have to seal it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My sweet child, Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have seen everything then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a lot of information\Nfor you to take in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, you should go inside and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit. They just keep coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Godo, at this rate, we can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your wits about you.\NWe have to find a way through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I commend you.\NThat was a long time to hold them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you couldn't\Nget rid of me that easily. Haha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,According to our reconnaissance,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,most of the remaining Grotesqueries\Nhave been eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We should clean up\Nthe last few stragglers as fast as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Miyo. I hope you slept well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like\Nyour ability's rampage is over then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even have to say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just seeing that expression tells me\Neverything I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then,\Nsince you've returned to the Usubas,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,we ask that you please wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been passed down through generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the maiden of Dream-Sight can\Nwear these garments.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,For the clothes you arrived in,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I will personally see that\Nthey're taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to fret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.31,0:09:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As I was freed from my nightmares,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my body gradually recovered\Nas the days passed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Time went slowly in this place,\Nas a gilded birdcage is still a cage.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Being parted from Lord Kudo,\NI only missed him more.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My feelings for him grew\Nequal to my regret.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd always known\Nbut I couldn't find the words that day.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.46,0:10:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one at fault.\NThis is all because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not hungry, Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I assume\Nthat I have yet to be forgiven?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps\Nyour room doesn't suit your taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is the food ill-suited to your palate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can have them remake it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please, if you would\Ngive me just a bit of guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give me back\Nthe kimono with the cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo had given that to me as a gift,\Nand it is very precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really mean you can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.88,0:10:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,May I just\Nspeak to Lord Kudo one time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:11:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling I was wrong.\NThat I was wrong about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm still too ashamed\Nto see him just yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I should give him an apology, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll say\Nyou want to leave this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We've waited...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,for so--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how long\NI've been waiting for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea how happy I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How elated I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect you, so let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my dear, it's my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,All that I want is to see Lord Kudo again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to say what I couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,say what I should have said\Nfrom the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We have rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rules set by our ancestors\Nthat we still faithfully uphold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"You must never use\Nyour last name with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.86,0:12:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage partners are\Nonly accepted within the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not make any close friends\Nor even take on a lover."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The Usuba's duty
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is to subdue other gift-users\Nwho step out of line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But not a single time since I was born\Nhave we ever been called into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We can follow every rule to perfection,\Nand yet it may not lead to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Usubas no longer have a purpose,\Nwe just sit here and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole life, I wanted a role\Nthat only I could take on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When the maiden\Nof Dream-Sight first appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,a member of our family\Nwith supernatural abilities
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,was specifically chosen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to risk their lives\Nprotecting her from any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As of this morning,\Nthat duty was passed on to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll likely take on\Nthe role of husband too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I am begging you, Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow my to fulfill my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stay here. I want to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This mission is mine, and I could\Nnever entrust it to anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had assumed...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}based on what I'd learned\Nthat we were alike.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Empty shells who had no purpose,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who wanted meaning\Nbut were never given an opportunity.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The horde of Grotesqueries is done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it, boys, we won!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.19,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Godo. Return to the initial formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll reorganize the reconnaissance team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:14:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Godo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.98,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How have you\Nfound your time here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is there anything\Nyou feel inconvenienced by?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, is there truly no way for me\Nto see Lord Kudo just one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts to say this,\Nbut no, it is not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's just for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Just one?\N- Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're reminding me of Sumi.\NShe was stubborn like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I hadn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,pushed Sumi away all those years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have lost my daughter\Neven before she passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life as my grandchild\Nwould have been far different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing like what you lived through.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my fault\Nand for all the hardships you endured,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I are family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Family that's related by blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens,\Nwe will be here to help and support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be shy about it.\NPlease rely on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never had family like you.\NIt's so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell me to rely on you,\Nbut what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even understand\Nwhat being a family is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For sure, I'm disappointing\Neveryone around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not understanding any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so bad that\NI even managed to anger Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that was a lot of nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry if I was rambling.\NYou didn't need to hear all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.08,0:16:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes me happy\Nto hear how you really feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you allow me to speak\Nas your grandfather
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,for just a moment, Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it true that being a family\Nmeans sharing the burdens
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we can't handle on our own together?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Share the burdens?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}In relying on someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}you aren't simply passing\Nthe weight of the world onto their back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I think relying on others\Nmeans sharing that load.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Things that we know would be too heavy\Nfor one person alone to carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You can disappoint family\Nor even make them angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But the bonds\Nof family will never be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when my mother left this house\Nagainst your wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was furious back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't deny that I took it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you come\Nto hate my mother for what she did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of father\Nwould I be if I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,More than feeling unforgiving,\NSumi's well-being was what I cared about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I deeply regret how I handled things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too caught up\Nin protecting what I thought I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The price for that mistake was\Nlosing my daughter forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, Miyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as I loved Sumi\Nwith my whole heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I hold you just as dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason our family managed to survive\Nwas Sumi getting married,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,which lead to giving birth to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I wish it were sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm happy\Nthat we could meet like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My grandfather feels\Nthe same way that I do.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We both said things we regretted\Nto people we deeply care for.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The guilt is a burden\Nthat we both must bear.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mother was doing her best,\Nall because she wanted me to be happy.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someday,\Nyou're going to need this power.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it should be your choice to use it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, you were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I can tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems Sumi's seal\Nhas been completely lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.82,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I just received\Na message from the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudo... is defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo is what?\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a Grotesquerie.\NHis unit was ambushed, and he went down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have all the details yet,\Nbut it sounded like a severe injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.63,0:19:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo, please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo is in trouble.\NI have to go see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be kept away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not allow you to leave this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then don't.\NI'm going to go either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid\Nthat I haven't been too clear with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a reason\Nthat you're being kept here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has\Na vested interest in your staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.88,0:20:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no interest\Nin lying to her any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A deal was made with the Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.55,0:20:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Emperor lent his hand{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}in fulfilling\Nthe Usuba's longstanding wish.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reclaiming the maiden of Dream-Sight.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In exchange,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all contact between you and anyone else\Nwith supernatural abilities is forbidden.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was the Emperor's order{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to seal the maiden\Nof Dream-Sight's existence away.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would he...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nwhat His Majesty is intending.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I defy him,\Nwe all may be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You will also be subjected\Nto his punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Know that this isn't me giving up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In the same way\Nyou won't give up on Kiyoka Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I've also made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go and see him, don't you?\NThere are things you must do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.24,0:21:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been decided.\NI will be traveling with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to make sure you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness sake! If you two must...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you are dear to me,\Nmy precious grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.17,0:21:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my duty as your grandfather\Nto support the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, go on. Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Kudo...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have to be okay.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.91,0:22:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.78,0:22:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did the Commander\Nrisk his life for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.79,0:22:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.88,0:22:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness! I'm so glad you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I was worried that was\Nthe last time you'd see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You were separated so suddenly back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I thought you might not...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.90,0:23:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miss Hazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know he'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I'm not giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyo, there's a chance that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.83,0:23:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}waking up Kiyoka might be\Nsomething you're able to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.79,0:23:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You may be able\Nto use your Dream-Sight ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}My ability, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't say it'll definitely work,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}but it's better than not trying, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.18,0:23:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If there's anything I can do,\NI have to try!
